snippet.title: Harvest Moon: A Wonderful Life Special Edition ♥ 1
snippet.description:
☆☆ My new life begins! ☆☆

One of my all time favourite games has finally been released for the PS4! Hopefully I can do everything in this game.. 

Plus - PLATINUM! (〃^∇^)ﾉ ♥

Personal playthrough, no commentary.

Broadcasted live on Twitch -- Watch live at https://www.twitch.tv/shannontronbonne
